de.rwth.i2.attestor.graph.morphism

Interface MorphismChecker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractVF2MorphismChecker, VF2EmbeddingChecker, VF2IsomorphismChecker, VF2MinDistanceEmbeddingChecker, VF2PreconditionChecker

    public interface MorphismChecker
    A MorphismChecker takes two graphs, called pattern and target, and computes all graph morphisms from the pattern graph into the target graph.
    Author:
    Christoph

    • Method Detail

      • run

        void run(Graph pattern,
         Graph target)
        Sets the pattern and target graph and searches for the first graph morphism. This method is not reentrant.
        Parameters:
        pattern - The pattern graph.
        target - The target graph.

      • hasMorphism

        boolean hasMorphism()
        Returns:
        True if and only if at least one Morphism has been found after calling run().

      • getMorphism

        Morphism getMorphism()
        Returns:
        The found Morphism or null if no Morphism has been found (yet).
